A vintage-style illustration of a whimsical, elongated rectangular camera with an unconventional organic flowing design, featuring curved biomorphic shapes and vibrant coral-red coloring, floating against a dreamy backdrop of softly layered bokeh circles in warm amber, teal, and cream tones, the camera appearing almost alive with fluid art nouveau curves, surrounded by multiple translucent overlapping photograph frames showing the same garden scene at different focal depths, muted sepia and ochre color palette with pops of saturated red, textured like aged photographic paper with subtle grain and warm vignetting at the edges
